## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(docs_cy, content_transformer(tolower)):
## transformation drops documents
# Remove numbers
docs_cy <- tm_map(docs_cy, removeNumbers)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(docs_cy, removeNumbers): transformation
## drops documents
# Remove english common stopwords
docs_cy <- tm_map(docs_cy, removeWords, stopwords("english"))
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(docs_cy, removeWords, stopwords("english")):
## transformation drops documents
# Remove your own stop word
# specify your stopwords as a character vector
# Remove punctuations
docs_cy <- tm_map(docs_cy, removePunctuation)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(docs_cy, removePunctuation): transformation
## drops documents
# Eliminate extra white spaces
docs_cy <- tm_map(docs_cy, stripWhitespace)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(docs_cy, stripWhitespace): transformation
## drops documents
# Text stemming
docs_cy <- tm_map(docs_cy, stemDocument)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(docs_cy, stemDocument): transformation drops
## documents

m_cy <- as.matrix(dtm_cy)

## transformation drops documents
